There is no evidence of a more recent overall FDA approval for any other company through December 2024; GlaxoSmithKline remains the manufacturer[1].

- GlaxoSmithKline plc is listed on the New York Stock Exchange (NYSE) under the ticker symbol **GSK**.
- The opening stock price for GSK on the FDA approval date of dostarlimab (April 22, 2021) was **$38.35**.

The more effective regimen in trial NCT02775006 contains dostarlimab. The most recent overall FDA approval for dostarlimab (up to December 2024) was granted to GlaxoSmithKline plc (GSK), which is listed on the NYSE under the symbol GSK. The opening stock price on the FDA approval date was $38.35.
